column3: Primary Care at Northwest Outpatient Medical Center
column5: The first drive thru COVID-19 testing site for UW Medicine patients is now open. At this time it's not your typical retail drive-thru
column7: Dr. Thomas Hei. UW Medicine set up shop in a parking lot Monday in Northgate at their Northwest Outpatient Medical Center. Staff said it's the vanguard site and they hope to add others in the future.
